metadata.name: Bi Siren
metadata.description:
Part of the METAPRIDE LAND 2022 Collection

Bi as in madly in love with myself and letting that abundance spill over & around me.  
Bi as in endless invitations for connection, reflection, and pleasure.  
Bi as in I’m a siren, and you will drown in my divinity and enjoy it, bitch.

Being bi to me means I can be attracted to anyone, regardless of gender or gender expression. I’m attracted to nuance, kindness, spirit, curiosity, wisdom, and chemistry.
